    "Moreover, the utilization of AI algorithms in assessment processes enhances transparency.",
    "This approach affords students a lucid grasp of the evaluative criteria, methodologies, and their application to individual scenarios.",
    "For instance, certain academics have developed a framework for certifying learning outcomes grounded in blockchain technology, leveraging its inherent characteristics of public verifiability, authenticity of content, and resistance to alteration, thereby ensuring a true and precise documentation of learners' educational trajectories (Wu et al., 2018).",
    "Evaluators can scientifically validate learners' accomplishments by examining the recorded data, thereby furnishing a transparent, equitable, and objective certification of achievements.",
    "This level of clarity enables students to more thoroughly understand the basis of their assessments and facilitates the pursuit of clarification or justification of the results."
